ðŸ“Š Data Description

The dataset used in this project consists of 12 columns representing marketing campaign performance data across customers, demographics, platforms, and products.
It is structured to support campaign-level analysis, customer behavior insights, and KPI calculations.

ðŸ—‚ Dataset Columns
Date Time____ Date and time when the campaign activity was recorded
Customer____Unique identifier or name of the customer
Age Group____Customer age segment (e.g. 18â€“24, 25â€“34, 35â€“44, etc.)
Gender____Customer gender
Country____Customerâ€™s country or campaign location
Product____Category	Category of the promoted product (e.g. Smartphones, Laptops, Accessories)
Campaign____ID	Unique identifier for each marketing campaign
Ad Platform____Advertising platform used (Google, Facebook, Instagram, Twitter)
Impressions____Number of times the ad was displayed
Clicks____Number of clicks generated by the ad
Conversions____Number of successful conversions
Conversion Value____Monetary value generated from conversions

